1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,780
=Episode 2=

3
00:01:00,799 --> 00:01:03,399
(The first trial was a breeze.)

4
00:01:03,399 --> 00:01:05,120
(But where did he go?)

5
00:01:06,879 --> 00:01:08,200
May I ask,

6
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,159
why

7
00:01:09,159 --> 00:01:11,239
is Lord Nine-Thousand
nowhere to be seen?

8
00:01:11,239 --> 00:01:12,680
His Lordship's whereabouts

9
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:13,959
are not for you to ask.

10
00:01:20,159 --> 00:01:21,000
(Nanfeng Pavilion)
Rumor has it

11
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,680
(Nanfeng Pavilion)
that on his way back today,

12
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:23,719
he was ambushed.

13
00:01:23,719 --> 00:01:24,879
Is that true?

14
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,480
Lord Nine-Thousand

15
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:28,879
was ordered to bring the Zhao
Holy Maiden to His Majesty.

16
00:01:28,879 --> 00:01:30,719
General Rong Xiu must be threatened.

17
00:01:31,319 --> 00:01:32,680
Are you insane?

18
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,040
That Holy Maiden,

19
00:01:34,040 --> 00:01:37,239
to me, is just a hostage
to control the Zhao Tribe.

20
00:01:39,040 --> 00:01:40,400
(This marriage alliance)

21
00:01:40,959 --> 00:01:42,959
(is only meant to control my tribe.)

22
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:44,599
(What matters now)

23
00:01:44,879 --> 00:01:47,159
(is to enter the palace
through this Lord.)

24
00:01:51,959 --> 00:01:53,239
I have no grudge against you.

25
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:54,359
Why did you hit me?

26
00:01:54,359 --> 00:01:55,959
You love showing off.

27
00:01:55,959 --> 00:01:57,239
Always taking the lead.

28
00:01:57,239 --> 00:01:58,439
You should know the cost.

29
00:01:58,959 --> 00:01:59,879
Boring.

30
00:02:01,599 --> 00:02:02,840
Who said you could leave?

31
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,640
Seriously?

32
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,280
How could she?

33
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,040
What happened?

34
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:07,120
What's wrong?

35
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:09,479
(A noble's daughter,)

36
00:02:10,360 --> 00:02:11,319
(you deserve this.)

37
00:02:11,879 --> 00:02:12,840
Stop, please!

38
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:16,319
Rong Xiu recently acquired a treasure

39
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:19,159
and will present it to the Emperor
in three days.

40
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:22,680
Since your Divine Power is so potent,

41
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,919
(Rong Xiu, Grand General of Kun)
you will investigate it for me.

42
00:02:24,919 --> 00:02:26,580
(Rong Xiu, Grand General of Kun)

43
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:29,240
But the general's mansion
is heavily guarded.

44
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,759
How do I get in?

45
00:02:30,759 --> 00:02:32,520
I can get you inside.

46
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,120
This is your second trial.

47
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:37,039
The second trial from me.

48
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,560
From now on,

49
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:40,840
I'll be counting on you, General.

50
00:02:44,879 --> 00:02:46,439
Kill the general!

51
00:02:47,039 --> 00:02:48,319
Let me refill that for you.

52
00:02:51,439 --> 00:02:52,000
Please.

53
00:02:54,120 --> 00:02:54,520
General!

54
00:02:59,240 --> 00:02:59,919
How dare you!

55
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:10,840
General.

56
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:11,759
Done.

57
00:03:12,439 --> 00:03:13,199
This jade,

58
00:03:13,199 --> 00:03:14,759
exquisitely carved,

59
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,240
will surely

60
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,360
delight His Majesty

61
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:18,039
and bring

62
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:19,319
great favor upon you.

63
00:03:19,319 --> 00:03:21,080
He will reward you handsomely.

64
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:24,199
Framing Jiang Yusang

65
00:03:24,199 --> 00:03:26,000
is simply too easy,

66
00:03:26,479 --> 00:03:27,199
little sister.

67
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:29,000
(In this memory,)

68
00:03:29,199 --> 00:03:30,520
(there's someone who harmed my sister.)

69
00:03:33,039 --> 00:03:33,800
(Rong Zhaohua, Imperial Consort Rong)
Zhaohua.

70
00:03:34,240 --> 00:03:35,719
(Rong Zhaohua, Imperial Consort Rong)
This is a Zhao Tribe Gu worm.

71
00:03:36,479 --> 00:03:38,039
With this,

72
00:03:38,039 --> 00:03:39,479
His Majesty will believe

73
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:42,000
that Jiang Yusang, that witch,
tried to poison him.

74
00:03:43,159 --> 00:03:44,879
You dare compete with me?

75
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,560
I'll make your life a living hell.

76
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:48,759
It was her.

77
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:53,039
She killed my sister.

78
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:54,719
Brother,

79
00:03:55,439 --> 00:03:57,360
you've been so good to Zhaohua.

80
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,960
Ever since I joined the Rong family,

81
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:00,360
you've always looked after me.

82
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:03,800
Zhaohua,

83
00:04:04,159 --> 00:04:05,199
in my heart,

84
00:04:05,919 --> 00:04:07,199
you are my own sister.

85
00:04:07,719 --> 00:04:09,039
Whatever you wish for,

86
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,840
I will make it happen.

87
00:04:13,599 --> 00:04:14,759
Jiang Yusang,

88
00:04:14,759 --> 00:04:16,680
you ungrateful woman!

89
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,600
You've been lying to me all along!

90
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,720
(Zhu Yunqi, Emperor of Kun)
The fire of vengeance in your heart

91
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:24,000
never died out!

92
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,240
Your Majesty,

93
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:27,839
why would I poison your meal?

94
00:04:27,839 --> 00:04:29,480
Please see the truth!

95
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:32,240
You are the only Zhao
in the entire palace.

96
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,519
Who else could have planted

97
00:04:33,519 --> 00:04:34,959
this Zhao Gu worm?

98
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:35,879
Your Majesty,

99
00:04:36,319 --> 00:04:37,879
Jiang Yusang has been here
for three years.

100
00:04:37,879 --> 00:04:38,680
She never

101
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,040
let go of her hatred.

102
00:04:42,199 --> 00:04:43,000
Your Majesty,

103
00:04:43,279 --> 00:04:43,759
Your Majesty,

104
00:04:43,759 --> 00:04:44,600
I truly didn't!

105
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,360
Please listen!

106
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:46,800
Your Majesty,

107
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,079
Your Majesty!

108
00:04:50,199 --> 00:04:51,399
(Using a Gu worm to frame her?)

109
00:04:51,399 --> 00:04:52,879
(Such a despicable trick.)

110
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,199
(All of them)

111
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,279
(will pay with their lives.)

112
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,279
How dare you!

113
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:59,480
Spare me, General!

114
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,160
Guards!

115
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:00,959
Take him away!

116
00:05:00,959 --> 00:05:01,480
Yes!

117
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,560
Mercy, General!

118
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,079
General!

119
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:03,439
Move!

120
00:05:05,759 --> 00:05:07,240
She really has her ways.

121
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,360
Why are you staring at me?

122
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:19,959
Feng Liu.

123
00:05:20,279 --> 00:05:21,040
Help her out.

124
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:21,560
Yes.

125
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,360
General!

126
00:05:31,720 --> 00:05:32,439
Fire!

127
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,480
It's a red jade bi.

128
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:46,279
To make it seem divine,

129
00:05:47,079 --> 00:05:48,879
Rong Xiu had a master inscribe it.

130
00:05:49,279 --> 00:05:50,279
Who is that man?

131
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,519
I don't know.

132
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:54,879
All I saw

133
00:05:54,879 --> 00:05:56,560
was a man with a white beard.

134
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:58,759
The knife used for carving,

135
00:05:58,759 --> 00:06:00,160
its handle is made of amber.

136
00:06:01,399 --> 00:06:02,000
Understood.

137
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:02,839
(Nanfeng Pavilion)
You may go.

138
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:03,560
(Nanfeng Pavilion)
My Lord.

139
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:05,420
(Nanfeng Pavilion)

140
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,920
My Lord,

141
00:06:07,519 --> 00:06:09,319
you must have long despised

142
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,680
General Rong Xiu.

143
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:13,680
Both of you are
the Emperor's right hands,

144
00:06:14,199 --> 00:06:15,360
yet he always...

145
00:06:16,399 --> 00:06:18,000
To be my needle,

146
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,639
the first thing you must learn

147
00:06:20,639 --> 00:06:21,879
is obedience.

148
00:06:29,020 --> 00:06:35,140
(Nanfeng Pavilion)

149
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:41,759
My Lord,

150
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,120
this Zhao Holy Maiden

151
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,600
was raised in a dungeon.

152
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,759
She's never seen the world.

153
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,759
Having just arrived,

154
00:06:48,759 --> 00:06:50,240
there's no way she knows Master Jin.

155
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:52,079
But the intel she gathered

156
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:53,279
matches exactly

157
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:54,319
what the Nanfeng spy found.

158
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:56,600
This Divine Power is truly mysterious,

159
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,800
able to peer into hearts.

160
00:06:58,439 --> 00:06:59,920
If I ever see her again,

161
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,839
I'll take the long way around.

162
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:04,199
She hasn't passed my trials yet.

163
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:08,560
Arrange for her to stay in my manor.

164
00:07:10,399 --> 00:07:11,680
Then tell her,

165
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,759
within one day,

166
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:16,839
she must obtain
this jade pendant from me.

167
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:19,399
That will be her final trial.

168
00:07:19,399 --> 00:07:20,040
Yes.

169
00:07:26,959 --> 00:07:28,759
Guess, Your Majesty,

170
00:07:30,480 --> 00:07:32,040
is this child in her belly

171
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,720
a boy

172
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,399
or a girl?

173
00:07:36,480 --> 00:07:37,439
I wager

174
00:07:37,439 --> 00:07:38,319
it's a boy.

175
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:41,279
Then I'll wager it's a girl.

176
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:43,560
Let's find out

177
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,639
once and for all

178
00:07:44,639 --> 00:07:46,240
what it is.

179
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,560
(Lin Lianshuang, Noble Lady Lin)
Mercy, Your Majesty!

180
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,879
(Lin Lianshuang, Noble Lady Lin)
This child is truly yours!

181
00:07:50,879 --> 00:07:51,319
And

182
00:07:51,319 --> 00:07:53,360
I'm already eight months along,

183
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:55,160
due any day now.

184
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,959
You dare keep His Majesty waiting?

185
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:57,720
Guards!

186
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:58,920
Cut her open!

187
00:07:58,920 --> 00:07:59,639
Your Majesty,

188
00:07:59,879 --> 00:08:01,000
then you'll see

189
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,639
that I am innocent!

190
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:04,639
Mercy!

191
00:08:04,639 --> 00:08:05,720
Your Majesty!

192
00:08:06,399 --> 00:08:07,199
Your Majesty!

193
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,759
Mercy!

194
00:08:08,759 --> 00:08:09,079
Go!

195
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,160
No!

196
00:08:12,759 --> 00:08:14,879
Mercy, Your Majesty!

197
00:08:16,680 --> 00:08:19,519
No!

198
00:08:19,519 --> 00:08:20,560
Your Majesty!

199
00:08:28,300 --> 00:08:32,020
(Zhu Heng, Lord of Zhenbei)

200
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:40,679
Reporting to Your Majesty,

201
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:41,720
it's a boy.

202
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,080
Your Majesty,

203
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,480
it seems I can never

204
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:48,320
win against you.

205
00:08:48,759 --> 00:08:50,120
You're mine.

206
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:51,840
My victories

207
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,240
are, of course,

208
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:55,320
shared with you.

209
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,960
Reap the crop before it ripens,

210
00:09:01,799 --> 00:09:02,559
the ear is empty,

211
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:03,759
and the stalk breaks.

212
00:09:04,159 --> 00:09:06,080
Pick the fruit before it's full,

213
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,200
the flesh is tart,

214
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,320
and the pit is bitter.

215
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:11,039
But some refuse to believe it.

216
00:09:11,039 --> 00:09:11,679
They delude themselves

217
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:13,200
that seeds in the earth

218
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:15,000
can sprout in winter

219
00:09:15,279 --> 00:09:17,240
against all seasons.

220
00:09:18,559 --> 00:09:19,440
Lord of Zhenbei,

221
00:09:20,559 --> 00:09:21,480
I heard

222
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,320
your consort

223
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:23,480
is also with child.

224
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,440
I beg you, see the truth!

225
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,799
I have no rebellious intent

226
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,200
as the memorial claims.

227
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:34,360
I never said you did.

228
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,120
Those ministers

229
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,759
love to chase shadows.

230
00:09:36,759 --> 00:09:37,559
They say

231
00:09:37,559 --> 00:09:38,799
you're amassing troops

232
00:09:39,279 --> 00:09:40,799
and planning a rebellion.

233
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,440
They're fools.

234
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,480
Rise.

235
00:09:45,279 --> 00:09:46,240
Thank you, Your Majesty.

236
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:48,559
I just want you to know,

237
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:50,360
don't let the rumors trouble you.

238
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,360
Since your lady is pregnant,

239
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:53,639
go home early

240
00:09:54,039 --> 00:09:55,440
and take good care of her.

241
00:09:55,440 --> 00:09:56,399
I understand.

242
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,279
Tomorrow,

243
00:09:58,000 --> 00:09:58,320
no,

244
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,799
today, I'll depart.

245
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:00,960
You may go.

246
00:10:05,919 --> 00:10:07,200
So, today...

247
00:10:08,120 --> 00:10:08,679
Your Majesty,

248
00:10:08,799 --> 00:10:09,519
Lord Nine-Thousand is here.

249
00:10:11,320 --> 00:10:12,120
Good.

250
00:10:12,559 --> 00:10:13,639
I'll change

251
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:14,840
and see him.

252
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:24,799
Your Majesty.

253
00:10:27,679 --> 00:10:29,000
Ah, my dear minister.

254
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,200
Greetings, Your Majesty.

255
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:36,600
I heard

256
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,799
you've brought back

257
00:10:37,799 --> 00:10:38,639
the Zhao Holy Maiden.

258
00:10:38,639 --> 00:10:40,440
Why not send her straight to the palace?

259
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:42,039
Your Majesty,

260
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,000
she is very crude.

261
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:46,399
She's not yet fit to serve you.

262
00:10:46,399 --> 00:10:48,080
I'll train her on your behalf.

263
00:10:48,759 --> 00:10:49,519
Besides...

264
00:10:51,600 --> 00:10:52,320
You may go.

265
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:57,759
Besides,

266
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,600
I know Your Majesty prefers discretion

267
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:01,360
and wants to let this woman

268
00:11:01,360 --> 00:11:02,919
enter the palace unnoticed,

269
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,679
I have

270
00:11:04,679 --> 00:11:06,440
placed her among the noble ladies.

271
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:09,000
This way, fewer will know.

272
00:11:09,279 --> 00:11:10,279
And if anyone finds out,

273
00:11:10,279 --> 00:11:11,399
I have ways

274
00:11:11,399 --> 00:11:12,799
to make them keep quiet.

275
00:11:12,799 --> 00:11:14,639
You always know my heart.

276
00:11:14,639 --> 00:11:15,759
Then this matter

277
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:17,600
is in your hands.

278
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,639
Rest assured, Your Majesty.

279
00:11:25,279 --> 00:11:27,279
This eunuch
from the Noble Ladies' Palace

280
00:11:27,919 --> 00:11:30,120
impregnated my Lady Lin.

281
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:31,080
Just now,

282
00:11:31,639 --> 00:11:33,480
I cut out his tongue.

283
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:34,840
My dear minister,

284
00:11:35,279 --> 00:11:36,279
help me think,

285
00:11:36,279 --> 00:11:38,000
what else can I do to him?

286
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:56,399
What a lowly handsome servant.

287
00:12:00,559 --> 00:12:03,480
I dare to ask for this servant.

288
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:05,279
Let me send him to the Nanfeng Pavilion

289
00:12:05,279 --> 00:12:06,879
and train him myself.

290
00:12:06,879 --> 00:12:08,039
Your Majesty...

291
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:12,000
Being favored by Lord Nine-Thousand

292
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,360
is your good fortune.

293
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:15,480
He's yours.

294
00:12:16,639 --> 00:12:17,639
Thank you, Your Majesty.

295
00:12:35,900 --> 00:12:37,300
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

296
00:12:37,780 --> 00:12:39,220
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

297
00:12:39,420 --> 00:12:42,540
♪No one knocks upon the mountain gate♪

298
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:46,660
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

299
00:12:49,620 --> 00:12:51,340
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

300
00:12:51,340 --> 00:12:52,860
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

301
00:12:53,220 --> 00:12:56,620
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

302
00:12:56,620 --> 00:13:00,620
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

303
00:13:01,780 --> 00:13:04,940
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

304
00:13:04,940 --> 00:13:08,500
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

305
00:13:08,500 --> 00:13:10,820
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

306
00:13:10,820 --> 00:13:15,020
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

307
00:13:15,460 --> 00:13:17,100
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

308
00:13:17,100 --> 00:13:18,620
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

309
00:13:18,620 --> 00:13:21,820
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

310
00:13:22,220 --> 00:13:24,140
♪In dreams, it's you♪

311
00:13:24,140 --> 00:13:25,540
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

312
00:13:25,540 --> 00:13:28,860
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

313
00:13:28,860 --> 00:13:32,260
♪I can't forget
the stars in your eyes♪

314
00:13:32,260 --> 00:13:35,820
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

315
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:39,060
♪In this mortal world,
there is only us♪

316
00:13:39,060 --> 00:13:42,500
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
